# Normalize line endings: store LF in the repo and check out LF on every
# platform. Without this, GitHub's Windows runners (core.autocrlf=true) check
# out CRLF, and the flows.toml line-surgery tests — which embed a text fixture
# via a triple-quoted string that then carries the file's line endings —
# parse-fail on the stray \r. eol=lf overrides core.autocrlf per path.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Keep common binaries untouched (none are committed today, but be explicit).
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.ico  binary
*.zip  binary
*.exe  binary
*.dll  binary
